{"tid":1916970,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【武漢肺炎】鍾南山最新估計疫情延至6月","createTime":"2020-03-09T08:02:31.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-13T01:39:05.000Z","uid":184679,"like":28,"dislike":81,"uniUserReply":131,"replies":[{"pid":"64f7a05eda857eafc88428981aaee2a4711f511f","tid":1916970,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-03-09T08:02:31.000Z","msg":"國家衞健委高級別專家組組長鍾南山此前表示，中國內地的新冠肺炎疫情將於4月底受控。針對全球疫情發展，他今天作出最新預測，指疫情預計至少延續到6月。<br />\n<br />\n鍾南山稱，新冠病毒的防控重點將由輸出轉為輸入，而廣東省的國際交往特別多，所以要加強邊檢邊境檢測的措施，而且要制訂從國外疫區赴華的措施，做好必要的隔離。對疫情嚴重的國家，廣東省可能要對外援助，包括防護、試劑和治療技術。<br />\n<br />\n上海復旦大學附屬華山醫院感染科近日舉辦網上論壇，鍾南山發表最新研究成果，指目前已研發一種新的檢測方法，名為恒溫擴增晶片，可對多患者同步檢測，分別新冠病毒和甲型、乙型流感，或其他現存病毒。<br />\n<br />\n<pre><code data-type=\"\">https://china.hket.com/article/2585105/%E3%80%90%E6%96%B0%E5%86%A0%E8%82%BA%E7%82%8E%E3%80%91%E9%8D%BE%E5%8D%97%E5%B1%B1%E4%BC%B0%E8%A8%88%E5%85%A8%E7%90%83%E6%96%B0%E5%86%A0%E7%96%AB%E6%83%85%E3%80%80%E5%BB%B6%E8%87%B36%E6%9C%88?mtc=30008</code></pre>"},{"pid":"3a233ff6ff236157a663589278ca1904141ee50b","tid":1916970,"uid":204539,"like":45,"dislike":1,"score":44,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-09T08:04:57.000Z","msg":"聽日再估<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5eb198a126bfedfbefec1bb8ccd8ab146c2cd134","tid":1916970,"uid":225130,"like":84,"dislike":1,"score":83,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-09T08:05:33.000Z","msg":"1至12月都估哂啦比佢"},{"pid":"f99012f547af0739ed4bbafd73e95de1599f8c2e","tid":1916970,"uid":159870,"like":30,"dislike":0,"score":30,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-09T08:05:44.000Z","msg":"之前又話4月<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1912a7403a7f1beec75d5aae770fd9566fe37b66","tid":1916970,"uid":135277,"like":31,"dislike":0,"score":31,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-03-09T08:06:03.000Z","msg":"2月履<br />\n4月<br />\n6月<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e7d8bbf882674954bb8363ac